title: New Mexico Resource GIS program, Oil Fields ,New Mexico, 2007
name: New Mexico Resource GIS program, Oil Fields ,New Mexico, 2007
description:
An inventory of the names and locations of oilfields, mines, dams, towers, and other man-made structures in New Mexico. Extracted from the USGS Geographic Names Information System.

This dataset is a subset of the original dataset found at the New Mexico Resource GIS program, and includes only the data on Oil Fields. 
data was reprojected from a state plain system.
